{
  "video_id": "OEkT14RBzDI",
  "title": "Automated Economy Explained: Mechanics of a Basic Income",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 710.0,
      "end_time": 5319.0,
      "text": "In 122 BC, Gaius Gracchus initiated a policy"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 5319.0,
      "end_time": 8681.0,
      "text": "that would later be known as &quot;Bread and Circuses.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 8681.0,
      "end_time": 11285.0,
      "text": "Roman landowners had slowly but surely"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 11285.0,
      "end_time": 15176.0,
      "text": "replaced their workers with cheap slaves from the colonies."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 15176.0,
      "end_time": 19098.0,
      "text": "This resulted in high unemployment of the Roman population."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 19098.0,
      "end_time": 21387.0,
      "text": "As the empire found itself in a situation"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 21387.0,
      "end_time": 24877.0,
      "text": "where production flourished but the population suffered,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 24877.0,
      "end_time": 28981.0,
      "text": "they introduced a policy of free grain and entertainment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 28981.0,
      "end_time": 31522.0,
      "text": "which led to new stability."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 31522.0,
      "end_time": 33982.0,
      "text": "Replace landowners with shareholders"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 33982.0,
      "end_time": 35678.0,
      "text": "and slaves with robots,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 35678.0,
      "end_time": 40680.0,
      "text": "and you will see where we are headed."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 40680.0,
      "end_time": 44660.0,
      "text": "You, my friend, probably love your job."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 44660.0,
      "end_time": 46495.0,
      "text": "It gives you status in society,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 46495.0,
      "end_time": 49935.0,
      "text": "an answer to the favorite small-talk  question, &quot;What do you do?&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 49935.0,
      "end_time": 53187.0,
      "text": "Maybe you even think it gives you a purpose in life."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 53187.0,
      "end_time": 57976.0,
      "text": "And, if nothing else, it puts some money into your bank account every month."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 57976.0,
      "end_time": 60269.0,
      "text": "But if you had the choice:"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 60269.0,
      "end_time": 64399.0,
      "text": "take the blue pill and keep working for your money as you&#39;ve always done,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 64399.0,
      "end_time": 69827.0,
      "text": "or take the red pill and you will never have to work a day in your life again."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 69827.0,
      "end_time": 71128.0,
      "text": "What do you do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 71128.0,
      "end_time": 73858.0,
      "text": "This is the question we are facing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 73858.0,
      "end_time": 77420.0,
      "text": "as we are increasingly  automating our economy."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 77420.0,
      "end_time": 80853.0,
      "text": "If the fact that the bots are coming for your job is news to you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 80853.0,
      "end_time": 83709.0,
      "text": "I suggest you watch this video by CGP Grey,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 83709.0,
      "end_time": 88656.0,
      "text": "one of many that will  bring you up to speed."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 88656.0,
      "end_time": 90310.0,
      "text": "In the simplified economic model,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 90310.0,
      "end_time": 93030.0,
      "text": "there are households,  which are people like you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 93030.0,
      "end_time": 95357.0,
      "text": "businesses, which are owned by people like you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 95357.0,
      "end_time": 97867.0,
      "text": "and a public sector, or the state."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 97867.0,
      "end_time": 100148.0,
      "text": "The households provide labor for the businesses"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 100148.0,
      "end_time": 102726.0,
      "text": "in exchange for an income by the businesses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 102726.0,
      "end_time": 104538.0,
      "text": "which they can pay to the businesses"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 104538.0,
      "end_time": 107989.0,
      "text": "in order to receive products and services of the businesses."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 107989.0,
      "end_time": 109976.0,
      "text": "And everyone pays taxes."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 109976.0,
      "end_time": 112835.0,
      "text": "Enter the Automated Economy."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 112835.0,
      "end_time": 115273.0,
      "text": "The first thing we need to do to adjust this model"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 115273.0,
      "end_time": 119178.0,
      "text": "is cross out the labor connection between households and businesses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 119178.0,
      "end_time": 122408.0,
      "text": "because businesses will get their labor from the bots."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 122408.0,
      "end_time": 126885.0,
      "text": "The average Joe won&#39;t be working a regular job, through no fault of his own."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 126885.0,
      "end_time": 128338.0,
      "text": "He has a good education,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 128338.0,
      "end_time": 133674.0,
      "text": "but there is just no field in which he can compete against the best bots out there."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 133674.0,
      "end_time": 136460.0,
      "text": "We won&#39;t be referring to him as &quot;unemployed,&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 136460.0,
      "end_time": 139627.0,
      "text": "much like we don&#39;t refer to most people as &quot;not a movie star&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 139627.0,
      "end_time": 141047.0,
      "text": "or &quot;not an athlete.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 141047.0,
      "end_time": 144733.0,
      "text": "His situation will be the status quo."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 144733.0,
      "end_time": 146444.0,
      "text": "Without an income from businesses"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 146444.0,
      "end_time": 148125.0,
      "text": "households can&#39;t pay taxes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 148125.0,
      "end_time": 150111.0,
      "text": "but even worse, can&#39;t spend money,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 150111.0,
      "end_time": 153252.0,
      "text": "thus causing an eventual collapse of the entire system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 153252.0,
      "end_time": 154312.0,
      "text": "and we don&#39;t want that"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 154312.0,
      "end_time": 157710.0,
      "text": "because wealth creation through production and consumption"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 157710.0,
      "end_time": 161172.0,
      "text": "is largely responsible for our well-being."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 161172.0,
      "end_time": 165232.0,
      "text": "The most widely suggested way to fix the chain at this point"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 165232.0,
      "end_time": 169650.0,
      "text": "is a Universal Basic Income (in short, UBI),"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 169650.0,
      "end_time": 173359.0,
      "text": "a state-distributed payment to cover your basic needs."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 173359.0,
      "end_time": 174597.0,
      "text": "&quot;Hold on there,&quot; you think."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 174597.0,
      "end_time": 176277.0,
      "text": "&quot;This sounds a lot like communism!&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 176277.0,
      "end_time": 177794.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not. Bear with me."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 177794.0,
      "end_time": 179236.0,
      "text": "The elephant in the room is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 179236.0,
      "end_time": 181694.0,
      "text": "where does the state get enough money"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 181694.0,
      "end_time": 184164.0,
      "text": "to pay every citizen a monthly income?"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 184164.0,
      "end_time": 185505.0,
      "text": "In a communistic system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 185505.0,
      "end_time": 188784.0,
      "text": "the answer would be the state just owns all production."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 188784.0,
      "end_time": 191380.0,
      "text": "But in a capitalistic Automated Economy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 191380.0,
      "end_time": 192279.0,
      "text": "not so!"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 192279.0,
      "end_time": 194679.0,
      "text": "Anyone can start and own a business,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 194679.0,
      "end_time": 198401.0,
      "text": "and the state will have to get its share  through taxes."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 198401.0,
      "end_time": 199521.0,
      "text": "With that in mind,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 199521.0,
      "end_time": 201617.0,
      "text": "let&#39;s go back to our model."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 201617.0,
      "end_time": 203044.0,
      "text": "Who do you think has been"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 203044.0,
      "end_time": 206417.0,
      "text": "the greatest beneficiary of automation so far?"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 206417.0,
      "end_time": 207859.0,
      "text": "You might be inclined to say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 207859.0,
      "end_time": 210219.0,
      "text": "&quot;The households! Because they get free money!&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 210219.0,
      "end_time": 213619.0,
      "text": "But that &#39;free money&#39; is really just a replacement"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 213619.0,
      "end_time": 217720.0,
      "text": "for what they&#39;ve gotten before when there were still jobs to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 217720.0,
      "end_time": 220318.0,
      "text": "So getting it without work sure is an advantage,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 220318.0,
      "end_time": 224021.0,
      "text": "but they aren&#39;t the biggest winners in this new system."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 224021.0,
      "end_time": 226369.0,
      "text": "The correct answer is: the businesses."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 226369.0,
      "end_time": 230689.0,
      "text": "They won&#39;t have to pay any employees anymore, remember?"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 230689.0,
      "end_time": 232785.0,
      "text": "This saves them a fortune."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 232785.0,
      "end_time": 235748.0,
      "text": "A business&#39;s largest expense by far"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 235748.0,
      "end_time": 237708.0,
      "text": "is usually people."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 237708.0,
      "end_time": 240452.0,
      "text": "All this money is now saved."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 240452.0,
      "end_time": 242317.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s why under the old,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 242317.0,
      "end_time": 244212.0,
      "text": "or rather current, system"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 244212.0,
      "end_time": 248918.0,
      "text": "a gradual move towards more automation results in two things:"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 248918.0,
      "end_time": 251398.0,
      "text": "a buildup in a business&#39;s cash reserves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 251398.0,
      "end_time": 253197.0,
      "text": "and a growing income gap"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 253197.0,
      "end_time": 255196.0,
      "text": "as ever-more wealth is distributed"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 255196.0,
      "end_time": 257006.0,
      "text": "among fewer employees,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 257005.99999999997,
      "end_time": 260038.99999999997,
      "text": "things which we can already observe today."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 260039.0,
      "end_time": 262907.0,
      "text": "So that&#39;s why in a  capitalistic Automated Economy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 262907.0,
      "end_time": 267205.0,
      "text": "there will simply have to be a  higher tax on company profits."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 267205.0,
      "end_time": 269933.0,
      "text": "And the entire system is financed."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 269933.0,
      "end_time": 271245.0,
      "text": "And the best thing is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 271245.0,
      "end_time": 273205.0,
      "text": "if we play our cards right,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 273205.0,
      "end_time": 274814.0,
      "text": "everybody wins!"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 274814.0,
      "end_time": 277917.0,
      "text": "Shareholders of the businesses  still end up with higher profits,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 277917.0,
      "end_time": 281776.0,
      "text": "and citizens can live on  a steadily increasing UBI."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 281776.0,
      "end_time": 283687.0,
      "text": "And it makes sense that everyone wins,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 283687.0,
      "end_time": 287617.0,
      "text": "because the entire system has become so much more efficient."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 287617.0,
      "end_time": 290852.0,
      "text": "We have an automated workforce  that runs on electricity cost."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 290852.0,
      "end_time": 293868.0,
      "text": "Instead of monkeys working an average 40-hour week,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 293868.0,
      "end_time": 295452.0,
      "text": "the bots are now running the show"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 295452.0,
      "end_time": 298395.0,
      "text": "at 168 hours per week."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 298395.0,
      "end_time": 299416.0,
      "text": "They don&#39;t get sleepy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 299416.0,
      "end_time": 300381.0,
      "text": "they don&#39;t need breaks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 300381.0,
      "end_time": 302311.0,
      "text": "and they make way fewer mistakes."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 302311.0,
      "end_time": 303802.0,
      "text": "You can live in a nice place,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 303802.0,
      "end_time": 305682.0,
      "text": "which is designed and built by bots,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 305682.0,
      "end_time": 307662.0,
      "text": "and buy some of the products you like,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 307662.0,
      "end_time": 309420.0,
      "text": "which are manufactured by bots."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 309420.0,
      "end_time": 312286.0,
      "text": "All that you can do on your basic income."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 312286.0,
      "end_time": 316637.0,
      "text": "And as GDP grows,  meaning economic output simply increases,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 316637.0,
      "end_time": 320927.0,
      "text": "your UBI gets higher  and your property gets better."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 320927.0,
      "end_time": 322418.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s a simplified model."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 322418.0,
      "end_time": 323379.0,
      "text": "The complete model,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 323379.0,
      "end_time": 326749.0,
      "text": "which includes value-added taxes and savings and trade,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 326749.0,
      "end_time": 329109.0,
      "text": "is a story for another time."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 329109.0,
      "end_time": 334938.0,
      "text": "But when the heat is in place, the rest of the body can work."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 334938.0,
      "end_time": 336728.0,
      "text": "Once we know the destination,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 336728.0,
      "end_time": 338941.0,
      "text": "we need to find a way to get there."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 338941.0,
      "end_time": 342072.0,
      "text": "This transition isn&#39;t going to happen overnight,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 342072.0,
      "end_time": 344457.0,
      "text": "but gradually over many years."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 344457.0,
      "end_time": 347485.0,
      "text": "The transition to industrialization had its downsides,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 347485.0,
      "end_time": 350058.0,
      "text": "and we should try to avoid such."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 350058.0,
      "end_time": 354698.0,
      "text": "So we need to put in place the right mechanics for it to be smooth."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 354698.0,
      "end_time": 358798.0,
      "text": "One such mechanism could be using automation indices."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 358798.0,
      "end_time": 360846.0,
      "text": "This idea is still completely hypothetical,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 360846.0,
      "end_time": 362576.0,
      "text": "but here is how it works."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 362576.0,
      "end_time": 365603.0,
      "text": "Automation indices measure the level of automation"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 365603.0,
      "end_time": 369086.0,
      "text": "some organization has reached over time."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 369086.0,
      "end_time": 370774.0,
      "text": "There would be two of them:"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 370774.0,
      "end_time": 373524.0,
      "text": "a business automation index (in short BAI),"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 373524.0,
      "end_time": 376843.0,
      "text": "and a national automation index (in short NAI)."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 376843.0,
      "end_time": 379408.0,
      "text": "The BAI determines how much automation"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 379408.0,
      "end_time": 381318.0,
      "text": "a particular company has reached,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 381318.0,
      "end_time": 385450.0,
      "text": "and is used to calculate the taxes they have to pay."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 385450.0,
      "end_time": 388395.0,
      "text": "For example, a company with a BAI of 1"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 388395.0,
      "end_time": 390246.0,
      "text": "has reached complete automation"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 390246.0,
      "end_time": 392934.0,
      "text": "and falls into the highest tax bracket"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 392934.0,
      "end_time": 394564.0,
      "text": "of a corporate base tax,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 394564.0,
      "end_time": 396615.0,
      "text": "which is simply today&#39;s corporate tax"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 396615.0,
      "end_time": 399841.0,
      "text": "plus 100 percent of an automation tax,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 399841.0,
      "end_time": 401237.0,
      "text": "which is around the same."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 401237.0,
      "end_time": 403547.0,
      "text": "A company with a BAI of 0.5"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 403547.0,
      "end_time": 405731.0,
      "text": "has reached half its automation potential"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 405731.0,
      "end_time": 407536.0,
      "text": "and falls into a medium tax bracket,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 407536.0,
      "end_time": 408807.0,
      "text": "of a corporate base tax"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 408807.0,
      "end_time": 412477.0,
      "text": "plus another 50 percent of the automation tax rate."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 412477.0,
      "end_time": 413597.0,
      "text": "&quot;Great!&quot; you think."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 413597.0,
      "end_time": 418434.0,
      "text": "&quot;But how on Earth do you calculate, or  determine, the BAI for a specific company?&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 418434.0,
      "end_time": 419998.0,
      "text": "I know you will hate to hear this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 419998.0,
      "end_time": 422365.0,
      "text": "but that is also a story for another time."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 422365.0,
      "end_time": 426505.0,
      "text": "All I can tell you is that everything that&#39;s needed to calculate the BAI"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 426505.0,
      "end_time": 430265.0,
      "text": "can already be found in a company&#39;s financial statements today."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 430265.0,
      "end_time": 432685.0,
      "text": "What about the national automation index?"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 432685.0,
      "end_time": 435356.0,
      "text": "The NAI is calculated using"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 435356.0,
      "end_time": 437340.0,
      "text": "a weighted average of all the BAIs"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 437340.0,
      "end_time": 438824.0,
      "text": "of a country&#39;s businesses"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 438824.0,
      "end_time": 442550.0,
      "text": "to determine the automation of the national economy as a whole."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 442550.0,
      "end_time": 447430.0,
      "text": "It is used to adjust the Universal Basic Income on a yearly basis."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 447430.0,
      "end_time": 448931.0,
      "text": "Using such mechanics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 448931.0,
      "end_time": 453081.0,
      "text": "countries could pay a Universal Income starting today."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 453081.0,
      "end_time": 454508.0,
      "text": "It would start out very low,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 454508.0,
      "end_time": 456692.0,
      "text": "as even our most advanced economies"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 456692.0,
      "end_time": 458779.0,
      "text": "are still caught up in old structures."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 458779.0,
      "end_time": 460779.0,
      "text": "But even at 50 dollars a month,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 460779.0,
      "end_time": 464647.0,
      "text": "we would have set the first cornerstone for our transition."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 464647.0,
      "end_time": 466485.0,
      "text": "And once the mechanics are in place,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 466485.0,
      "end_time": 470673.0,
      "text": "countries should be racing to get from here to there."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 470673.0,
      "end_time": 471621.0,
      "text": "Thanks for watching!"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 471621.0,
      "end_time": 473202.0,
      "text": "If you&#39;ve watched this entire video,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 473202.0,
      "end_time": 475672.0,
      "text": "you might think about supporting me on Patreon."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 475672.0,
      "end_time": 477229.0,
      "text": "Creating these videos has become"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 477229.0,
      "end_time": 479451.0,
      "text": "a very time-consuming hobby of mine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 479451.0,
      "end_time": 483801.0,
      "text": "and any support will go directly towards improving quality and upload frequency."
    },
    {
